hadiths[25]{hadithnumber,text}:
2385,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang mein Sharik tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, apne oont ke barey mein tumhari kya raey hai. kya tum usey bechogey? maine kaha haan, chunanche oont maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bech diya aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina pahunchey. to subah oont ko lekar main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey uski qeemat ada kar di."
2386,"ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se ghalla aik khas muddat (ke qarz par) khareedaa , aur apni lohey ki zirah uske paas rahan rakh di."
2387,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo koi logon ka maal qarz ke taur par ada karne ki niyat se leta hai to Allah Taala bhi uski taraf se ada karega aur jo koi na dene ke liye ley, to Allah Taala bhi usko tabah kar dega."
2388,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab dekha, aap ki murad Uhud pahaad (ko dekhney) se thi. to farmaya ke main ye bhi pasand nahi karunga ke Uhud pahaad soney ka ho jaey to usmein se mere paas aik Dinar ke barabar bhi teen din se zyada baqi rahe. siwa us Dinar ke jo main kisi ka qarz ada karne ke liye rakh loon. phir farmaya, (duniyaa mein) dekho jo zyada (maal) waley hain wahi mohtaaj hain. siwa unke jo apne maal w daulat ko yun aur yun kharch karein. abu-Shihaab rawi ne apne samney aur daain taraf aur baain taraf ishara kya, lekin aisey logon ki tadaad kam hoti hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya yahin thahrey raho aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi door aagey ki taraf badhey. maine kuchh awaz suni (jaisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi se baatein kar rahe hon) maine chaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho jaun. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farman yad aaya ke'' yahin us waqt tak thahrey rehna jab tak mein na aa jaaun'' iske baad jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine puchha ya Rasulullah! abhi maine kuchh suna tha. ya (raawii ne ye kaha ke) maine koi awaz suni thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tum ne bhi sunaa! maine arz kya ke haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere paas Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aaey they aur keh gaey hain ke tumhari ummat ka jo shakhs bhi us haalat mein marey ke wo Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraataa ho, to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. maine puchha ke agarche wo is tarah (ke gunaah) karta raha ho. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha ke haan."
2389,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar mere paas Uhud pahaad ke barabar bhi sona ho tab bhi mujhey ye pasand nahi ke teen din guzar jayen aur us ( soney (ka koi hissey mere paas reh jaey. siwa uske jo main kisi qarz ke dene ke liye rakh chhodun. uski riwayat Saleh aur Aqeel ne Zohri se ki hai."
2390,"aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apne qarz ka taqaza kya aur sakht-sust kaha, sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko saza deeni chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey kehney do. saahibe-haq ke liye kehney ka haq hota hai aur usey aik oont khareed kar de do. logon ne arz kya ke iske oont se (jo us ne aapko qarz diya tha) achi umr hi ka oont mil raha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wahi khareed ke usey de do. kyonke tum mein achchha wahi hai jo qarz ada karne mein sabse achchha ho. (hadees aur baab ki mutaabiqat zahir hai)"
2391,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs ka intiqal hua (qabr mein) us se sawal hua, tumharey paas koi neki hai? usne kaha ke main logon se khareed-farokht karta tha. (aur jab kisi par mera qarz hotaa) to main maaldaaron ko mohlat diya karta tha aur tang-daston ke qarz ko maaf kar diya karta tha is par uski bakhshish ho gaee. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine yahi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai."
2392,aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apna qarz ka oont maangney aaya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke usey iska oont de do. sahaba ne arz kya ke qarz denewaale ke oont se achi umr ka hi oont mil raha hai. is par us shakhs (qarz denewaale) ne kaha mujhey tum ne mera pura haq diya. tumhen Allah tumhara haq pura pooraa de! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey wahi oont de do kyonke behtreen shakhs wo hai jo sabse zyada behtar tariqa par apna qarz ada karta ho.
2393,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aik shakhs ka aik khas umr ka oont qarz tha. wo shakhs Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se taqaza karne aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey oont de do. sahaba ne talash kya lekin aisa hi oont mil saka jo qarz-khaah ke oont se achi umr ka tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wahi de do. is par us shakhs ne kaha ke aap ne mujhey mera haq poori tarah diya Allah aapko bhi iska badla pura pooraa de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein behtar aadmi wo hai jo qarz ada karne mein bhi sabse behtar ho.
2394,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjide-Nabawi mein tashrif rakhtey they. Misar ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne chasht ke waqt ka zikr kya. (ke us waqt khidmate-nabawii mein hazir hua) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke 2 rakaat Namaz padh lo. mera Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par qarz tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey ada kya, balke zyada bhi de diya."
2395,unke walid ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) Uhud ke din Shahid kar diye gaey they. un par qarz chala aa raha tha. qarz khaahon ne apne haq ke mutaalbey mein sakhti ikhtiyar ki to main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farma liya ke wo mere baagh ki khajoor ley lein aur mere walid ko maaf kar dein. lekin qarz khaahon ne us se inkar kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein mere baagh ka mewa nahi diya aur farmaya ke ham subah ko tumharey baagh mein aaeingey. chunanche jab subah hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey baagh mein tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darakhton mein phirtey rahe aur uske mewey mein barkat ki dua farmatey rahe. phir maine khajoor todii aur unka tamam qarz ada karne ke baad bhi khajoor baqi bach gaee.
2396,"jab unke walid Shahid huey to aik Yahudi ka tees wasq qarz apne uper chhod gaey. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se mohlat maangii, lekin wo nahi maanaa. phir Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey taake Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us Yahudi (Abu-Shaham) se (mohlat dene ki) sifarish karein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur Yahudi se ye farmaya ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ke baagh ke phal (jo bhi hon) us qarz ke badley mein ley ley. jo unke walid ke uper uska hai, us ne us se bhi inkar kya. ab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baagh mein dakhil huey aur is mein chaltey rahe phir Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke baagh ka phal tod ke iska qarz ada karo. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif laey to unhon-ne baagh ki khajoorein todiin aur Yahudi ka tees wasq ada kar diya. satrah wasq usmein se bach bhi raha. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey taake aapko bhi ye itlaa dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt Asr ki Namaz padh rahe they. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farigh huey to unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko itlaa di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski khabar ibne-khattaab ko bhi kar do. chunanche Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, main to usi waqt samajh gaya tha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baagh mein chal rahe they ke usmein zaroor barkat ho gaee."
2397,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein dua kartey to ye bhi kehtey ''aey Allaah! main gunah aur qarz se teri panah mangta hoon.'' kisi ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! aap qarz se itni panah maangtey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya ke jab aadmi maqrooz hota hai to jhoot boltaa hai aur wada karke uski khilaf warzi karta hai.
2398,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs (apne intiqal ke waqt) maal chhodey to wo uske waarison ka hai aur jo qarz chhodey to wo hamarey zimme hai.
2399,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, har momin ka main duniya w aakhirat mein sabse zyada qareeb hun. agar tum chaho to ye aayat padh lo ( النبي أولى بالمؤمنين من أنفسهم‏ ( '' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mominon se unki jaan se bhi zyada qareeb hain.'' isliye jo momin bhi intiqal kar jaey aur maal chhod jaey to chahiye ke waaris uske Malik hun. wo jo bhi hon aur jo shakhs qarz chhod jaey ya aulad chhod jaey to wo mere paas aa jayen ke unka wali main hun."
2400,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, maaldaar ki taraf se (qarz ki adaaeygi mein) taal matol karna zulm hai."
2401,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik shakhs qarz maangney aur sakht taqaza karne laga. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski goshmaalii karni chahi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey chhod do, haqdaar aisi baatein keh sakta hai."
2402,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ya ye bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, jo shakhs hoo-bahoo apna maal kisi shakhs ke paas pa ley jabke wo shakhs deewaaliya qarar diya ja chuka ho to saahibe-maal hi uska dusron ke muqaabley mein zyada mustahiq hai."
2403,"aik shakhs ne apna aik ghulam apni maut ke sath aazad karne ke liye kaha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us ghulam ko mujh se kon khareedtaa hai? Naeem-bin-Abdullaah ne usey khareed liya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski qeemat (aath (8) so dirham) wsool karke iske Malik ko de di."
2404,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi Israaeelii shakhs ka tazkira farmaya jisne doosrey Israaeelii shakhs se qarz maanga tha aur us ne aik muqarrara muddat ke liye usey qarz de diya. (jiska zikr pahley guzar chuka hai).
2405,"(mere waalid) Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid huey to apne peechhey baal bachchey aur qarz chhod gaey. mein qarz-khaahon ke paas gaya ke apna kuchh qarz maaf kar dein, lekin unhon-ne inkar kya, phir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unki sifarish karwaaii. unhon-ne iske bawajud bhi inkar kya. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (apne baagh ki) tamam khajoor ki qismein alag alag kar lo. azq-bin-Zaid alag, leen alag aur ajwa alag (ye sab umda qism ki khajooron ke naam hain) iske baad qarz-khaahon ko bulao aur main bhi aaoonga. chunanche maine aisa kar diya. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke dher par baith gaey aur har qarz-khaah ke liye maap shuru kar di. yahan tak ke sab ka qarz pura ho gaya aur khajoor isi tarah baqi bach rahi jaisey pahley thi. maano kisi ne usey chhuwa tak nahi."
2406,"aur aik martaba main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jihad mein aik oont par Sawar ho kar gaya. oont thak gaya. isliye main logon se peechhey reh gaya. itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey peechhey se maara aur farmaya ke ye oont mujhey bech do. Madina tak is par sawari ki tumhen ijazat hai. phir jab ham Madina se qareeb huey to maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat chaahii, arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! maine abhi nai shadi ki hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kunwari se ki hai ya bewa se ? maine kaha ke bewa se. mere walid Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid huey to apne peechhey kai chhoti bachchiyaan chhod gaey hain. isliye maine bewa se ki taake unhein taleem de aur adab sikhaatii rahe. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, achchha ab apne ghar jao. chunanche main ghar gaya. maine jab apne maamun se oont bechney ka zikr kya to unhon-ne mujhey malaamat ki. isliye maine unse oont ke thak janey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke waqia ka bhi zikr kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke oont ko maarney ka bhii. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina pahunchey to main bhi subah ke waqt oont lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey oont ki qeemat bhi de di, aur wo oont bhi mujhey wapas bakhsh diya aur qaum ke sath mera (maal ghaneemat ka ( hissey bhi mujh ko bakhsh diya."
2407,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik shakhs ne arz kya ke khareed-farokht mein mujhey dhokaa de diya jata hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab khareed w farokht kya karo, to keh diya karke koi dhokaa na ho. chunanche phir wo shakhs isi tarah kaha karta tha."
2408,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah Taala ne tum par maan (aur baap) ki nafarmani ladkiyon ko zinda dafn karnaa, (waajib huquq ki) adaaeygi na karna aur (doosron ka maal naajaaiz tareeqe par) daba lena haram qarar diya hai. aur fuzool bakwaas karne aur kasarat se sawal karne aur maal zaaye karne ko makruh qarar diya hai."
2409,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna, tum mein se har fard aik tarah ka Hakim hai aur uski raiyat (zimmedaarii) ke barey mein us se sawal hoga. to badshah Hakim hi hai aur uski raiyat ke barey mein us se sawal hoga. har insan apne ghar ka Hakim hai aur us se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. aurat apne shauhar ke ghar ki Hakim hai aur us se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. khaadim apne aaqa ke maal ka Hakim hai aur us se uski raiyat (zimmedaarii) ke barey mein sawal hoga. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ye sab maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha aur main samajhta hun ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya tha ke mard apne walid ke maal ka Hakim hai aur us se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. to har shakhs Hakim hai aur har shakhs se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga."
